{"id":2364,"type":6,"name":"Mad Men (season 3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f7/e2/2364_HtPtM.jpg","rating":{"total":15,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":2,"7":3,"8":3,"9":3,"10":3},"score":7.9},"summary":"两年来载誉无数的AMC剧集《广告狂人》(Mad Men)的第三季。\r\n六十年代，广告业蓬勃兴起，个性的、专业的、大手笔的、以性为卖点的……各种各样的广告开始轰炸人们的神经，刺激人们的消费欲望。混战之中，一家高调的广告公司斯—特灵-库柏异军突起，从香烟广告到选举广告，无所不能。公司拥有才华横溢的创意总监的唐-德雷柏(Don Draper，乔-汉姆饰演)，野心勃勃觊觎德雷柏职位的助理拜特-坎贝尔(Bette Campbell，文森特-卡吉瑟饰演)，继承家业的女老板雷切尔-麦肯(Rachel Menken，玛吉-希福饰演)...他们将面对如鲨鱼搏斗般残酷的竞争，他们之间也将展开爱恨情仇的纠结。\r\n同时，广告业的极度膨胀开始引发社会的变革，这部片子也反映了在美国六十年代的性、伦理、生育、宗教史事。(转)","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>广告狂人 第三季</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>7</li><li><span>集数: </span>13</li><li><span>开始: </span>2009年8月16日</li><li><span>结束: </span>2009年11月8日</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情</li><li><span>导演: </span>Tim Hunter / Alan Taylor</li><li><span>编剧: </span>Matthew Weiner</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.amctv.com/originals/madmen/</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt1439792</li>","collection":{"wish":7,"collect":24,"doing":3},"tags":[{"name":"美剧","count":6},{"name":"AMC","count":5},{"name":"60年代","count":2},{"name":"Weiner","count":2},{"name":"Matthew","count":2},{"name":"广告狂人","count":2},{"name":"TV","count":1},{"name":"US","count":1},{"name":"剧情","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":13848,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/13848","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"Out of Town","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2009-08-16","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":13849,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/13849","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"Love Among the Ruins","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2009-08-23","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":13850,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/13850","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"My Old Kentucky Home","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2009-08-30","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":13851,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/13851","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"The Arrangements","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2009-09-06","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":13852,"url":"http://b